text: Morimospasma tuberculatum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939.BioLib.cz - Morimospasma tuberculatum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1939
